The first batch of personal pension financial products are on sale and can be held for as short as 360 days - China News Service
The first batch of personal pension financial products went on sale
7 products from institutions can be selected, and the shortest holding period is only 360 days
The personal pension financial product is finally launched.
On February 10, China Financial Management Network released the first list of personal pension wealth management products, and seven personal pension wealth management products from ICBC Wealth Management, ABC Wealth Management and China Post Wealth Management were officially launched.
At this point, the &quot;shelf&quot; of personal pension accounts finally has four types of products: personal pension savings, personal pension wealth management, personal pension insurance, and personal pension public funds.
According to reports, the first batch of personal pension wealth management products are all public net value open-end products, including 5 newly issued products and 2 existing products. Except for one product which is a mixed product, the other 6 products are all fixed income products.
Beijing Youth Daily reporters saw that four of the five newly launched products were from ICBC Wealth Management, all of which were fixed-income products. The shortest holding periods were 365 days, 540 days, 720 days and 1,080 days, respectively. The corresponding performance benchmarks (annualized) were 3.70% - 4.20%, 4.10% - 4.60%, 4.40% - 4.90%, and 5.25% - 5.75%, respectively.
The remaining new product is &quot;Youyin Wealth Tianyi Hongjin Shortest Holding 1095 Days No. 1&quot;, which is also a fixed income product. It started fundraising on February 10 and ended on February 19. The risk level is level two.
Of the two existing products, one is the ABC Wealth Management &quot;ABC Tongxin Lingdong&quot; 360-day technological innovation RMB wealth management product, which is a mixed investment product with a risk level of three.
Another existing product is &quot;Youyin Wealth Tianyi Hongjin Shortest Holding 365 Days No. 1&quot;, a fixed income type. It started fundraising on December 30 last year, officially started operation on January 4 this year, and the cumulative net value on February 8 was 1.0011.
According to the &quot;Opinions of the General Office of the State Council on Promoting the Development of Personal Pension Funds&quot;, the financial products that personal pension account funds can invest in include bank wealth management, savings deposits, commercial pension insurance, public funds, etc.
The launch of the first batch of personal pension wealth management products marks that personal pension investors can officially purchase wealth management products through their personal pension fund accounts.
In November last year, the China Banking and Insurance Regulatory Commission formulated the &quot;Interim Measures for the Management of Personal Pension Business of Commercial Banks and Wealth Management Companies&quot;.
The Measures stipulate that participants can purchase personal pension products such as personal pension savings, personal pension wealth management products, personal pension insurance products, and personal pension public fund products through their personal pension accounts.
Subsequently, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the Ministry of Finance, and the State Administration of Taxation issued a notice to clarify that the individual pension system will be launched and implemented in 36 pilot cities and regions including Beijing, Tianjin, Shijiazhuang, Xiongan New Area in Hebei Province, and Jincheng City in Shanxi Province.
As of the end of 2022, the number of people participating in individual pension plans was 19.54 million, the number of payers was 6.13 million, and the total payment amount was 14.2 billion yuan.
Previously, banks participating in the pilot program only listed three types of products: personal pension savings, personal pension insurance products, and personal pension public funds.
Now that personal pension financial products are available, how should investors choose?
Experts from the R&amp;D department of Bank of Communications&#39; wealth management products said that compared with other personal pension products, pension wealth management products and personal pension wealth management products in the pilot phase have three characteristics.
First, stability. The risk management mechanism is more sound, the investment strategies and concepts are more stable, and independent custody by a third party other than the parent bank is implemented.
Second, long-term nature. During the pilot phase, the term of pension wealth management products is 5 years or more. For the personal pension wealth management products to be issued in the next step, the minimum holding period is 1 year in principle, and holding for more than 3 years is encouraged.
Third, it is affordable. The threshold for purchasing products is low, and the starting purchase point is generally 1 yuan, and some are as low as 0.01 yuan. The rates of product custody fees, management fees, etc. are more favorable.
Professionals point out that investors should make choices based on product features and their own risk tolerance.
Personal pension savings have the characteristics of longer term, higher interest rate and high security, and are suitable for people with weak risk tolerance; personal pension insurance products focus on protection, and are more suitable for people who cannot bear investment risks but can accept stable returns; personal pension wealth management products and public fund products do not guarantee principal or returns, and have certain investment risks, but the expected returns are higher, and are suitable for people with certain financial knowledge and higher risk tolerance.
