&quot;Fund E-account&quot; is here: CSRC authorizes the development of all funds under the name of investors to realize the collection and query - Economic Observer - Professional financial news website
Economic Observer reporter Chen Shan: The complicated channels for purchasing funds make it difficult to collect account information?
Always forgetting about the “secret fund”?
